snippet.title: Dome-King Cabbage X Asobu Indie Showcase
snippet.description:
I felt ridiculously humbled and grateful being surrounded by so many great titles in the Asobu Indie Showcase. Here is Dome-King Cabbage's segment. You definitely have to watch the whole showcase! https://youtu.be/qgasz7vpv48


If you'd like to follow the development of the game and receive periodic updates, please join my mailing list! https://mailchi.mp/5fed62db0791/join-the-cobysoft-collective
